{
  "id": "adv_bond_ski_01_03",
  "title": "白石沙季3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "実家ってやっぱり落ち着くわね\n千紗とも、ちょうどオフが重なっていて良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My home is always comfortable\nI'm glad Chisa and I had our days off at the same time",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "お互いお仕事もあるし\n一緒におうちで過ごすことって少なくなってたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We both have jobs‚ so\nwe don't get to spend much time together at home anymore",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "お母さんも喜んでくれてたし、お父さんが帰ってきたら\nごちそう作るって言ってたよ。今から楽しみだな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mom was so happy to see us‚ and said she'd make a special meal\nfor dad when he gets home. I'm already looking forward to it~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そうね\nそれまで何してようかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ me too\nWhat should we do until then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "テレビでも観る？　そういえば、昔はよく\n二人でアイドルの番組を観てたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Watch TV? Come to think of it‚ we used to\nwatch idol shows together a lot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5999987285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。夜遅い番組とか、千紗ってば「お姉ちゃんと\n一緒に観たい」って言って隣で観てたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. I used to watch late-night shows‚ Chisa would say‚\n'I want to watch it with saki-chan' and sit next to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "いつも途中でうとうとして、寝ちゃってたわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you always dozed off and fell asleep halfway through",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4666684469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.4666684469
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうだったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I did",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9333351136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.9333351136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "気づいたらいつも、お姉ちゃんが膝枕してくれてて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whenever I wake up‚ saki-chan always gave me a lap pillow",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.9666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふふ、またしてあげよっか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ should I do it again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7333351136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.7333351136
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "おいで、千紗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come here‚ Chisa",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.0666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えぇ！？　そ、それはさすがに恥ずかしいよぉ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeh!? W-Well‚ that's too embarrassing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.5666702271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "もう子供じゃないんだし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not a child anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあついでに、耳かきしてあげましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then as a bonus‚ I'll clean your ears too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.8666702271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "それならいいでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0287354152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（もしかして、お姉ちゃん……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Maybe‚ Saki-chan…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.8666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.8666702271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "（甘えてほしいのかなぁ……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Does she wants me to be pampered…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2832914353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "うん、じゃあ……ちょっとだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ then… just a little",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.2000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.2000035604
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.9999997457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ右耳から。痛かったら言ってね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ start with your right ear. Tell me if it hurts?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.066663615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ん……ふふっ、ちょっとくすぐったい……かも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… hehe‚ it's a little… ticklish…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4333302816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.4333302816
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ…………へくちっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… A-choo…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9666664124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.566663615
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、千紗はくすぐったがりね\nでも、あんまり動かないでね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ Chisa is so ticklish\nBut‚ try not to move too much‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.566663615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……誰でもくすぐったいよぉ……\n終わったら、私もお姉ちゃんにしてあげるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… Anyone would be ticklish…\nAfter that‚ I'll clean your ears‚ too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.5333302816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.5333302816
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私は大丈夫よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm fine",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4999969483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.4999969483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "奥の方、見ていくわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll check‚ deeper part",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shiraliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shiraliving-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.2666664124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあ次は、私の番だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then next‚ it's my turn",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3333318075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_ski_01_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、お姉ちゃん、ゴロンってして？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ saki-chan‚ lie down",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1333330791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "わ、私は大丈夫なんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm fine…",
        "id": ""
